<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width">
        <title>Home</title>
    </head>

    <body style="background:#EBD8DB; padding:20px; border-radius: 20px;">
        <p>Good day, <%= customerName %>,</p>
        <p>Thank you for supporting our business, G-cakes! Below is the breakdown of your orders and their complete details. You have 7 days to settle payment to avoid cancellation. </p>
        <p style="size:15px"><u>ORDERS SUMMARY:</u></p>
        
        <table style="width:60%">
        <tr>
        <% orderDetails.forEach(function(orders) { %>
            <tr>
                <td><strong><%= orders.name %></strong></td>
                <td style="text-align:right">&#8369;<%= orders.price %> x <%= orders.quantity%></td>
            </tr>
            <% if (orders.type == 'cake') { %>
                <% if (orders.cakeNumber== '') { %>
                    <tr><td style="padding-left:50px;"><%= (orders.flavor).replace(/^./, (orders.flavor)[0].toUpperCase()); %> <%= orders.size %></td></tr>
                    <tr><td style="padding-left:50px;"><%= orders.dedication %></td></tr>
                <% } else { %>
                    <tr><td style="padding-left:50px;">Shape: <%= orders.cakeNumber %></td></tr>
                <% } %>
            <% } else if (orders.type == 'cupcake') { %>
                <tr><td style="padding-left:50px;"><%= (orders.flavor).replace(/^./, (orders.flavor)[0].toUpperCase()); %></td></tr>
                <tr><td style="padding-left:50px;"><%= (orders.design).replace(/^./, (orders.design)[0].toUpperCase()); %></td></tr>
                <tr><td style="padding-left:50px;"><%= (orders.frosting).replace(/^./, (orders.frosting)[0].toUpperCase()); %></td></tr>
            <% } else if (orders.type == 'cookie') { %>
                <tr><td style="padding-left:50px;"><%= (orders.design).replace(/^./, (orders.design)[0].toUpperCase()); %></td></tr>
            <% } %>
        <% }) %>
        <tr>
            <td colspan="2" style="text-align:right;"><strong>Total: &#8369;<%= totalPrice %></strong></strong></td>
        </tr>
        
        </tr>
        </table>

        <p>Should you have any changes or concerns about your orders, please <strong>reply to this email</strong>. Please note that changes for your order will no longer be entertained after payment has been sent.</p>  
        <p>Below are the payment options:</p>
        <img style="height: 200px; width: 200px; margin-left: 20px;" src="cid:BPI"><img style="height: 200px; width: 200px; display: inline-block; margin-left: 20px;" src="cid:GCASH">
        <p>Please settle payment and proof of payment within <strong>7 days</strong> to avoid cancellation. After proof of payment has been sent, you may ask for updates about your order by replying again to this email thread.</p>
        <p>Thank you, <br>Gina from G-Cakes</p>
    </body>

</html>
